{
  "stem": "43.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So-- so I-- when-- when Hitler was in Russia, when he-- he want to take Russia-- so they took even-- even the-- the cook away from the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So I was cook.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I was the cook.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I got a Russian [? lady ?] on the-- and-- and it was the second [? end. ?] And the Armenian many Jews came.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I could help.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I-- I took-- I cook a little more soup, a little more [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It wasn't too much, but [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And there, the-- I got a Russian girl from a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So she took all the food to them, not [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, she was a Russian-- a Russian girl, a goy, no.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I-- I was [INAUDIBLE] she sleeped with me in-- in one bed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we worked together-- a very nice person.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She helped so many [INAUDIBLE] come work in the fields for [INAUDIBLE] partisans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I try whatever I could.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I tried to--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The-- the Ukraine?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No Jews over there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody what-- what-- what [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I leave Ukraine and took [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Ukraine, was-- I [? heard ?] in the papers a piece of the first time when I-- I came to my-- to my-- to-- to our town before I left.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I-- we didn't-- I don't want to go to Russia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I-- I told [INAUDIBLE], [INAUDIBLE], I am going away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't want to Russia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I want to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I-- we must come the American zone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So and I-- in the night, I left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She wouldn't-- if she would tell the other people find me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So [INAUDIBLE] still the war ended.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I took this as a story also.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Can you hear more a little?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went out and I-- it was the soldiers going there.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
